{"tid":1931004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國政府內部文件：疫情將持續18個月 物資普遍短缺","createTime":"2020-03-18T02:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T02:41:04.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa44fdeaa43e5dee96bb89bef6183f37db7c911","tid":1931004,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"美國政府一份內部文件指，預料新型冠狀病毒疫情將持續18個月，令全美普遍出現物資短缺。美國《紐約時報》取得一份長達100頁的政府內部報告，評估疫情可能出現多個浪潮，影響醫療，緊急服務和基礎設施，部分州份和地方政府的基建和通訊將受到壓力，協調地方應對疫情的工作將面臨挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1274622&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1274622%26csid%3D261_367&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=ce915641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1274622&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"cd16c9ef91322d5e5195b3c1db14372fe3431143","tid":1931004,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa5e7c1af7219498606664f7b7f132c22a2167b","tid":1931004,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"香港人搶定物資先"}]}